Personally, I think everybody in LA shood have the shit beat out of them.. at least three times a day.  But, them I am a Comanche..not a wimpy cop.<br>
You should be grateful for guys like Caveman Cook.  If it weren't for guys like him..you street vendors of witch craft psychology would have no illiterate masses to gobble up your false credentials.  You may be able to impress some few ignorant victims with your thin veneer of psychological buzz words..but you are like the prostitute who treats herself for venereal disease.. you don't cure anything.. you just create mutations.  I shudder at the thought of what you may have done to some suffering people.<br>
It is obvious that not only do you lack honor..you have no sense of pride.  You have made a complete and total laughing stock of yourself on this site.  Don't flame at those who point out the fact that you are a fool!  You are the one who has and continues to make a fool of himself.  Have you no skills at processing feedback?<br>
I feel that the primary purpose of this site is to heal veterans of the Vietnam War, reveal historical facts and generally enlighten people to the horrors of war and its aftermath.  Perhaps then we can avoid war (if possible.. and it is not possible) or at least conduct them in a manner favorable to our interests.<br>
I have found that acceptance heals emotional wounds.  Here, on this site, I have discovered many new friends who are seeking a place to voice sensitive and painful issues.  <br>
Many young standup comedians, vulnerable and insecure, end their careers because of drunken dim witted hecklers..who have no wit!<br>
You are a heckler.. a disgusting distraction.. counter productive to any good work that might be accomplished here.<br>
I realize that you are so focused upon being somebody important that you cannot accomodate the fact that you are a miserable failure.  Your instant short cuts lead you to believe that you are far in lead of the group on the main road of life.  Fact is you are lost on a dirt road.  The reason you are alone is not because you are so far ahead of everyone.. but because you are so far behind.. in values and solid performance.<br>
A lot of back mail suggests that you are seriously ill.  I have been asked by several to let you play your silly games for the sake of your unstable condition.<br>
You remind me of diarreah in Vietnam.. something we couldn't fight..kill..or run from..it was just something that we had to live with.  The difference is.. we don't have to tolerate you and your sickness... but we do.  It's called free speech ...something we fought for..something you abuse but did not fight for.  We fought for freedom of religion.. you exercise a freedom from religion (there is a difference!)<br>
If you want to read or post here... at least try to curtail your lies, personal confrontations and filthy language.<br>
If you have any knowledge of psychology.. think back.  While you were screwing up by the number, your mother was forgiving you and brushing your hair.. the only way she knew how to love you.  You were robbed!  Instead of being taught boundaries.. you were given constant enabling comfort.  Your mother, loving you the only way she knew, created a pig.<br>
I feel sorry for you..for many reasons.. but I despised you and your actions.<br>
It is time for me to stop fighting Spatziareah and move on.
